PrecisEnactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF, 2002-1 - which eliminates tariffs on certain flexible plastic spouts, poly (vinyl chloride) and acrylontrile-butadiene rubber sheets, blankets used in offset printing machinery, automated fresh pork ham de-boning robots and pharmaceutical grade L-Tryptophan, and makes a number of other corrections to the Customs Tariff.

precis:
Enactment of an ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF, 2002-1 -
which eliminates tariffs on certain flexible plastic spouts, poly (vinyl
chloride) and acrylontrile-butadiene rubber sheets, blankets used in offset
printing machinery, automated fresh pork ham de-boning robots and
pharmaceutical grade L-Tryptophan, and makes a number of other corrections
to the Customs Tariff.
